These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, comedy, mystery, western
1. the person watching comedy movies is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching western movies is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching comedy movies##2
3. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | western | comedy | mystery |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, engineer, entrepreneur, designer
1. the manager is on the left of the designer##1
2. the engineer is in an odd position##4
3. the engineer is on the left or right of the manager##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Job   | engineer | manager | designer | entrepreneur |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, writing, rock-climbing, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is writing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Hobby   | traveling | magic-tricks | rock-climbing | writing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, coffee, mirinda
1. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
2. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4
3. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking coffee##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage   | cola | almond-milk | mirinda | coffee |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, train, subway, airplane
1. the person driving the helicopter is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Transport   | airplane | helicopter | subway | train |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, cycling, climbing, golf
1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
3. the person who's sport is climbing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |    4    |
| Sport   | climbing | basketball | golf | cycling |

