.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-14::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, musical, time-travel, sports
1. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
4. the person watching sports movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | sports | mystery | musical |

