.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-18::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, azure, yellow, orange
1. the person who likes yellow is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes azure is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who likes yellow is between the person who likes azure and the person who likes grey##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Color   | orange | grey | yellow | azure |

