.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, april, february, october
1. the person who's birthday is in april is the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's birthday is in january is in an even position##4
5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Birthday   | february | october | april | january |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, video-games, puzzles, filmmaking
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby   | writing | filmmaking | puzzles | video-games |

 